---
title: Crispy Falafel & Feta Tacos with Creamy Parsley Sauce plus Balsamic Onion & Tomato
description: Our fresh spin on a Mediterranean street food mainstay, these falafel-stuffed tacos are drizzled with creamy parsley sauce and sprinkled with feta cheese and balsamic pickled onion and tomato veggies for bright, tangy flavors. It all comes together so fast—less than 20 minutes from kitchen to table— that it’ll be a wrap before you know it!
